'''Maurice Dafydd''' was an 18th-century Welsh hymn-writer. His works include a booklet published in 1789, containing hymns such as 'Am graig I adeiladu...'. He is thought to have been a member of [[Bala, Gwynedd|Bala]] Congregational Church.
